      "date": "2013-03-12 17:07:19.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 3: I would prefer that you didn't submit this\n\n(5 inline comments)\n\nI think none of local objects (invisible above OSD should have FID), this may lead to all sorts of confusion in the future.\n\nI'd suggest the patch to fix OI scrub to look at  LMA and skip agent objects.",
