      "message": "Patch Set 3:\n\nAgree with Alex that lma_incompat needs to be set = and not |=. \n\nDi, it is worthwhile to look/test what happens on an old MDS when it hits an incompat object. It should hopefully still be able to list the name, but not the attributes I think?",
